<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.5.8">
<l>caṅku taṅku taṭaṅkaṭal kaṭaṉmallai yuḷkiṭantā yaruḷpurin</l>
<l>tiṅkeṉṉuḷ pukuntā yiṉippōyi nālaṟaiyō</l>
<l>koṅku ceṇpaka mallikai malarppulki yiṉṉiḷa vaṇṭu pōyiḷam</l>
<l>teṅkiṉ tātaḷaiyun tiruvāli yammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You lay in Kaṭalmallai near the wide sea where conches dwell;</l>
<l rend="indent">being merciful, you entered into me here.</l>
<l>If you go now, [what a] shame,</l>
<l>Lord of sacred Āli where sweet, young bees,</l>
<l rend="indent">having clung to fragrant champaka and jasmine [flowers],</l>
<l>Go and tumble in the pollen of young coconut trees.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
